<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-3681] AntBuilder calls maybeConfigure() on Task too early</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-3681</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;AntBuilder realizes (calls maybeConfigure() ) UnknownElement too early. Ant build listener need to have a chance for modifications to UnknownElement passed to listener via BuildEvent in taskStarted().&lt;br/&gt;
Related issue: GANT-91&lt;/p&gt;</description>
